project: to create a python based firewal

day1-3:
learned the basic concepts about networking downloaded the virtual box to use kali linux for better convenience
downloaded scapy and python3 was inbuilt within the kali itself

builded a basic network sniffing program using python (sniffer.py) to capture the packets along with parsing and headers, as well as prints source ip,destination ip,protocol and ports.
